  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> leek[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways and wash thoroughly to remove any grit from between the leaves, then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1644839529166-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1644839529166-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1644839529166-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1644839529166-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1644839529166-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tortiglioni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Tip: It doesn't need to be fully cooked, as it will go in the oven later!</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> tortiglioni </strong>and set it aside for later</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1644839541266-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1644839541266-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1644839541266-x700.jpg",
