    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and most of your <strong>goats' cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> cheesy stock</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes </strong>in half</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
