    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leeks have slightly softened, add your<strong> dried oregano</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
