    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> with the <strong>spinach </strong>and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min, stirring frequently, or until the sauce has thickened slightly</p>",
